Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:48.98,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}本字幕由澄空学园字幕组制作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:25.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に替わることで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:28.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}明日が近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:32.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前のことに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.96,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}心は傷ついた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:38.21,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:40.04,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}かなう時がいつか来るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:45.53,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:47.34,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:53.32,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}ないと誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:58.21,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に会える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:02.13,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返しめぐる運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:05.46,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえどんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:09.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して決してあきらめない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:10.96,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}明日またね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:12.89,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}その未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:16.68,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでもなくさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:20.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:22.20,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今君と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:25.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.63,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}つないだ手を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:33.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:25.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}用现在覆盖过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:28.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}未来就是这样步步走近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:32.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如此理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.96,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}却依旧心殇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:38.21,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那天你我所见的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:40.04,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}再一次拼凑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.60,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}愿望实现之时若能到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:45.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我再无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:53.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}即使被人嘲笑不切实际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:58.21,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}直到再见你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:05.46,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}纵使颠沛轮回的命运再艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:09.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我也绝对  绝对  不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:10.96,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:12.89,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那一份未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:16.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}让我们一直珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:20.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}一旦开始  再无休止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:22.20,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}现在我只愿和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:25.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}去瞭望梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}紧握的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:33.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}不会再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:38.11,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(600,302)}『遗失的未来』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  你又熬夜看望远镜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚啊  小时候的奏出现在梦里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭着问我「怎样才能抓到星星呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的奏真是可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都哭着说想要星星了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了你快吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏奏  佳织都变可靠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你快去重新倒一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  你也别呆着了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  佐佐木同学怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意中人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是帮我问问啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是受朋友所托啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己去问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  我要去问的话她肯定会误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是从小就在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  要是问了这问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都得活在微妙的氛围当中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  这个月她都拒绝三个人了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…一般来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说你们都住在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不会随口谈起类似的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木同学就跟你在同一屋檐下洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是每天每天每天每天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古典文学的作业是今天交？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  快给我抄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得帮我把佐佐木同学的入浴场景拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你抄作业的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是给你吃草莓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会被草莓收买的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉自己今天会被抽中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次会去La Mer买蛋糕给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要草莓蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢  先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  败给蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蛋糕么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  是蛋糕蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我能拿一个炸鸡块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示下友谊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果断拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  奏  现在不是吃便当的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的会长大人貌似在干一件exciting的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许需要帮手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等KENNY  我还没吃完饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  佳织也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说叫你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到不用我们出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说很遗憾我们来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华宫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐原来你在啊  什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…一开始就在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦您阻止下她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  大家都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在调停？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是疑问句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这些人扭打在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想着要劝劝来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意弄成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是话剧部的这些家伙先袭击过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们把我们的招牌给弄坏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西…没有是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但除了你们还会有谁干出这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啥？找茬是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先爽快地向对方道歉比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…这个不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}果然是你们做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你们就不用知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长还有副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们看好你们天文学会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是有事要拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是你来回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化节期间就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那边也当没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就简单说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维护治安算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是天文学会该干的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风纪委员干的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想把麻烦的事情推给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要干太危险的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长也说要尽可能采取和平手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是嘴上说说而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正会长肯定是想看戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就注定不可能会和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我会控制自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不要把我卷进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个到底是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的研究所那边已经帮忙调查过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样装神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  影研的照片也是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要调查那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是华宫会给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华宫会是学姐的粉丝会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  也就是一群对我言听计从的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是可以破例让奏和KENNY入会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}太好了  请我喝三杯果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}Oh My~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}KENNY可以让让吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  今年的文化节上天文学会要干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能创造一份美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是高中最后的文化节了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化节  啊  我也想叫上珍妮弗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My sweet heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna hold you tight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看照片嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是随便的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给你们决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏你完全没干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起学校活动我觉得看星星比较有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西的魅力在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星这种存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在是在发着光的但也可能其实已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这一瞬间看到的星星或许再也看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多让人激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个好主意  大家一起去看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给你们进行详细解说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦  反正很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那坐我家的车去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  奏  要不要做个天象馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的时候是模拟过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在桌子上就能看的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能做出更棒的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘一个大圆顶  做出满天的星星么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会蛮辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家齐心协力的话一定能做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然是会帮你的  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  让我们轰轰烈烈地给华宫学姐送终吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说法太不吉利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里有投影机和星座图可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆顶的材料和尺寸要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听不太懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的奏很Happy吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织真是懂如何让奏高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天说那段子不腻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了佳织只是青梅竹马而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理  圆顶能做多大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能尽量大些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要做不如搞个大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这教室的空间都用上的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理  预算能用多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是需要向学生会申请的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明刚才完全没有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真脏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚是想咬我的脚对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能穿条性感点的内裤么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么啊  这个…这个…色狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有东西要买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh  伤害大和抚子的行为让人不敢苟同哦  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追过去啊  真不懂体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要吃蛋糕吗蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人好好谈谈吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理你对奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢你哦  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是太笨了不会表达而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织你真是可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔道部跟空手道部的争执
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都按耐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏来这么麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空有柔道部这名号实际都是些流氓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都鹿如小心撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织你还是回活动室比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:11:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别小瞧人啊你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信不信我干掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我放手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文学会？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  学姐你什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从一开始就在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是我们社团的一年级生撞到了他们的二年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们就跑过来找麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  这事情太蠢了我都无语了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就不觉得丢人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手道部是正经社团不会动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是你们就来找事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那位佐佐木佳织还不是用饭局和便当收买了空手道部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人家把文化节上的表演时间给缩减了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是通过正当手段协商来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收买的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了表示感谢才给他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你撤回收买这个说法！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不许再乱来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义感太足强出头可是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  你先回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要生气到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候消消气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏你太耍赖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算学习再好体育再棒也不能老这样胡来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦  这样的你真的有在反省吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说长船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一副得意的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在表扬你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样  你们都要做一定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  华宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我有话想对您说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感觉好像在看什么不该看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这次就这样原谅你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不为例哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张红彤彤的Face是搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不是什么有意思的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然在食堂吃饭  真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  今天诗织阿姨大大的睡过了头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才跑来食堂而不是吃便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  话说是今天去看星星的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好  佳织的样子怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子  不知在生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  你可要多替佳织想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊  搞得这么正式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然  我也没办法再迈出步子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能清楚地看到星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织你不在可就不能算作「大家」了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  我是想和你一起去看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去活动室了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那里的四颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是秋季四边形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组成了天马座的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  风好舒服  好想睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  完全没在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我们的天象馆也能像这一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你是叫我搞一个出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  诺贝尔奖  亿万富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿珍妮弗不会被别的男人抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是祈愿一下胸部的成长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  住脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我错了  我错了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  你没有愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话我希望现在能有谁来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和平就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别浪费这么浪漫的氛围哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴有些渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想喝点热的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的时候我好像看到有自动售货机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝咖啡就可以了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织喝红茶可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个  我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏还真是让人操心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏也差不多该领退休金了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要吃苦头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理你就甘愿这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我又没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难受的时候就该吃点甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖  糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子  好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh  又是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望文化节能热热闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  会不会就这样飘起来然后被星空吸走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在说胡话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于又看到你不生气的脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像小孩子一样的闹别扭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要说声对不起  虽然还不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你们要出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到楼上去看一下剩余的物资
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  和KENNY两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪沙学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  她已经不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下记得要告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说才能让她这么春心荡漾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说了句「虽然还不太明白但我也要说声对不起」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这一句？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后佳织心情就变得这么好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  疼  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从心底对你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动室里的茶叶已经没了  我想去买一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶叶店很早就会关门的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是家人或兄妹的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是另一种的  喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那个  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  怎么了啊  突然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再当青梅竹马了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会生你的气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  也很重视佳织你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能一直和你在一起就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏你又耍赖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用现在  但一定要对我有交代哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会蛮辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家齐心协力的话一定能做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然是会帮你的  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  让我们轰轰烈烈地给华宫学姐送终吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说法太不吉利了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthquake？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这和地震的声音不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我就留在这里看门了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就分头调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  惨不忍睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道是哪个倒霉蛋来打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体模型？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织…
