Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:45.40,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:46.60,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}是做什么事情的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:47.50,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}被甩了吧
