Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:49.73,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}有关幽灵的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:51.55,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(200,200)}去抓日本幽灵吧
